---
title: Creamy Bacon & Pesto Penne with Apple Salad & Parmesan
description: The only way to improve the age-old family favourite, pesto pasta, is to add some crispy bacon and sharp Parmesan. With oh-so-many textures and well-loved flavours, this dish is sure to please the whole table!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nz-creamy-bacon-pesto-penne-514d1a44.jpg
